The '''Parvin E'tesami Literary Award''' ({{lang-fa|جایزه ادبی پروین اعتصامی}}) is an [[Iran]]ian [[literary award]] presented yearly since 2004. Every year, an award is given to the best Iranian authors on the birthday of the renowned Persian poet [[Parvin E'tesami]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.mehrnews.com/news/3685518|title=Parvin E'tesami Literary Award |author=|date= |website=[[Mehr News Agency]] |publisher= |language=Persian |accessdate=}}</ref>
