===Game===
A [[visual novel]] style [[dating sim]] game was released onto [[Android (operating system)|Android]] and [[iOS]] under the name {{nihongo|''Sanrio Danshi: Watashi, Koi wo, Shirimashita.''|サンリオ男子～わたし、恋を、知りました。～}} on September 13, 2016.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.4gamer.net/games/348/G034891|title=サンリオ男子～わたし、恋を、知りました。～|publisher=4gamer|accessdate=2018-01-13}}</ref> The theme song is "Fun! Fantastic Girl", produced by [[Elements Garden]] and performed by the voice actors of Sanrio Boys.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.4gamer.net/games/348/G034891/20161004017|title=「サンリオ男子」5人が歌う主題歌が実装。プロデュースはElements Garden|publisher=4gamer|date=2016-10-04|accessdate=2018-01-14}}</ref> Approximately 100,000 users downloaded the game during the first six days of release.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.4gamer.net/games/348/G034891/20160921143|title=「サンリオ男子～わたし、恋を、知りました。～」が6日間で10万DL突破|publisher=4gamer|date=2016-09-21|accessdate=2018-01-14}}</ref>

